{
  "stem": "1415.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She did give us a room in our own home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember-- I don't remember how many people we were in that room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we got the second room too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had two rooms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know how many of us were in those two rooms.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they were whoever came to our hometown.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We somehow managed to sleep on the floor, or wherever it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We-- we managed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we stayed there [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] until the war was over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when the war was over, apparently our names circulated everywhere because we were on the Red Cross list.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So when my brother found our name, he was already-- he got liberated I don't know when.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "After lib-- maybe when it was after the war, or just before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he found our name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was already in-- in Italy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was going to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was in Milano.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I remember because he wrote to us from Milano [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to tell us to wait for him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he put his name on the list, naturally.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And every day, we used to go to our-- there was one room in our hometown where they made it like the community room, and they posted all the things that came in that day.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they would post those lists, lists.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There were-- and one day, we found the list with his name on it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it-- it was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then we got-- we received a letter from him to say to wait for us-- for him in our hometown.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
